Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna do this all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I really thought I was gonna die, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It started blowing hot air at me all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's broken...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so hot I couldn't sleep all night...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well don't go compensating for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.15,0:00:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we have a song to polish before the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you dislike about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, how do I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds a bit too mainstream, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it, I've had it with your nitpicking. I'm out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Same here..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.15,0:01:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:55.08,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H0FFFFFF&\3c&H777777&\4c&HFFFFFF\i1\b1\fnSegoe Script\pos(1480,932)}A CRESCENT MOON CAME OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why didn’t you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You told me before something was bothering you about that new song.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not eating, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna die at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighborhood notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:21.95,TLNote,,0,0,0,,{\an8} TL Note: In Japan, sometimes neighborhoods have a bulletin/notice that circulates between residents, usually through the mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah right, our mailbox is damaged. Could you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good evening, it's Nina!\N- Sorry, we're not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I haven't even said anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, it's so cool here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop sucking in our cold air!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, it's not like you'll run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your voice down you public nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re way louder than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop ringing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool off and leave, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be so cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The AC guy said he'll only come next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And how is that my problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Momoka-san have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She does, but she works at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't yours a bit too weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}DON'T TOUCH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See, now {\i1}this{\i0} feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Much better than your old piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a piece of junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even turn it up, what else do you call that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It literally said "DO NOT TOUCH".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,both our ACs are out of commission at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don’t mind, we’d be grateful\Nif you'd let us cool off for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.56,0:04:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for a tiny little hour, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all this thing's fault, just for the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine. But just one ho-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,OOOOOOOOOUUUUURR?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Tomo-chan's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he really can't stand the heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t just let him out like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Powerful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one impressive apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:04:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's real nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she'll stop by since she works around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz346.6\pos(1028,792)}Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz346.6\pos(1116,240)}Momoka-san, the other three\N barged in here since their ACs broke. Want to come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz346.6\pos(972,440)}I work close to the Shinagawa\N Prince Hotel, I'll be done in 30 minutes and head over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well eat here together then, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SOUNDS GOOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And when did I agree to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you saying something about one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, just take the- oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, guess the last train's gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This was your plan all along, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, I even brought us some cards to pass the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's well-prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We never really had the chance to do something like this if you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, there's four of us, so-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be borrowing the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I got {\i1}Ametaro's Rail{\i0} too if you want. Wanna do the 100-year challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.14,TLNote,,0,0,0,,{\an8} Reference to the {\i1}Momotaro Dentetsu: Showa, Heisei, Reiwa mo Teiban!{\i0} Nintendo Switch game. The 100-year challenge is a very long game mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to stay here all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can think of a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Heading to bed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need me for your game night, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have complaints, I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Complaints? What made you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(1548,372)}{\i1}{\fnArial\fs100}The loser pays for the food! \NRupa: 20, Nina: 2, Subaru: 10{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is even going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, that's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to blame someone, blame my AC!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have at least tried to suck it up for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed some time in a convenience store,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I even sat on a bench doing nothing for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But being outside is super boring when you're broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s Tomo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she say anything about the song?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked like she had something to say back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a waste if it gets warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you think will happen if my grandmother sees it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's not like there will be any beer left in them by morni-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, he's calm and not venomous at a-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,SNAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAKE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, saved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of it! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's afraid of snakes, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a freaking snake! Are you all just completely fine with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In what world can four out of four girls be okay with snakes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a snake right behind you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:10.85,DefaultSpaced,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(912,700)}{\3c&HB89C27&\b0\i0\fnComic Sans MS\fs100}IT'S JUST A HAIRDRYER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She opened the-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Momoka-san!\N- Just get rid of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you break anything I'm the one who's gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We put it in Tomo-chan's room for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re going to break the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I. Said. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re too old for tantrums!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're seriously going to- \N- Nina, heads up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, out, NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Vexing, aren't they. Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Never come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- I’m hot...\N- And whose fault is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You get along so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No we don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I’m off to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of the snake, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-san said she's willing to keep it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I was a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, time to scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We should check on the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re gonna ditch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And why would we want to see your face outside of rehearsals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san said hanging out together is good for the band, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have time, want to watch me practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get my guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An acoustic guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine-san told me I should constantly practice if I want to get good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it's a good guitar, even though it's old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The second string's out of tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve been playing piano since you were little, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with it. Anyone can hear this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the guitar is amazing isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m actually starting to get callouses on my fingers from practicing so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still a bit off,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess that's the best you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you think? I thought I could try playing for our next concert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've really improved a lot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm all for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An extra guitar will definitely spice our sound up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Playing at a concert at your level? Are you serious?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not exactly my area of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, guitar isn't mine either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know music theory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's fine, for an amateur at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,An amateur?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't play on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to play on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing Diamond Dust's concert really made me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To stop relying on Momoka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and be able to stand proud next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With you all, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So if there's something I need to improve, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you just keep playing pretend like you are now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...even your entire life won't be enough for you to learn properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How many times do I have to tell you? Take it seriou-{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't judge us by your own standards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not all of us won piano awards as kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’m done with this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Wait-\N- You just shut up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were talking yesterday, and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten a bit cooler now, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn’t hurt to go without the AC for a bit sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can feel the gradual change in temperature on your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz332.1\pos(572,592)}Still hot in here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\frz332.1\pos(828,484)}Thank you for today
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Nina was happy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No way she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You got some nerve showing your mug here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I, uh, wanted your advice on something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, I promise I didn’t come for the AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I seriously need advice. Band-related advice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I’ll definitely pay you back (in 36 installments please). Iseri Nina.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Tomo say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That I might as well be playing pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that I'll never get anywhere like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, she sure didn't sugarcoat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's just how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it demotivate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's your reaction, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I kind of agree with Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I practiced a lot, so I thought I'm ready for the stage at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, even a year or two might not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially if you're trying to go pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're managing somehow, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo would probably have a ton of things to say about my playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But she never did, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because I never went out of my way to ask her to like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s a bit of a coward in that sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She prefers to keep her distance out of fear of being disliked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'll never approach you herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, if you approach her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a bit like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, you were like that at first too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I put him in a terrarium in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn’t eaten anything though, is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still at it, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru-chan gave me some feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just play on stage if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It disbanded?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to Tokyo and recruited members online
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to start a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how you two met?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There was also a guitarist and a drummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They both said they wanted to go pro, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's how it goes. Everyone says that at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, people who make it love to say
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that they didn’t do anything special to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Except if that were true, success would be within everyone’s reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And Tomo-chan is fully aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why she’s so strict with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought we were all on the same page,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so she became more and more demanding as time went.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still stayed with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She did say she wanted to go solo at one point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Her age was a bit of a problem though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A guarantor?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don’t want to contact my parents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I promise I won't be a burden.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s how we moved in together
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and created our duo Beni-Shoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We were lucky to get some offers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but she ended up wrecking it every time, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,she became afraid of saying what she really thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Afraid that if she does, it'll ruin things again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,About my playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it work live?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a bit late?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's eating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Being cautious and scared is fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but standing still won't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let’s take a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Still as hot as ever, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow, we're back to rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully it won't rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not wrong, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told her what she’s worth, period.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you suddenly change your mind after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Nina wants, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to play together with Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she came to you in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what everyone says.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm serious", "I want to get better", they all say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, they just want the praise that comes with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To sing whatever and however they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this, this, and this dangit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what I say you dumb fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing them play as a trio
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,made me understand something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they're far from perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,they still give it their all on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think what you've been looking for all along is exactly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see, I'll get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely enjoying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno, something's still bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:21:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As it is now, I think this song is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina Iseri: Rina Momoka Kawaragi: Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.47,0:22:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru Awa: Mirei Tomo Ebizuka: Natsu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa: Shuri Tomo Ebizuka: Natsu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Next up: "Wandervogel".{\i0}
